---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About — AB Brothers Construction"
  description="Licensed, insured, and built on referrals. AB Brothers Construction is a family-owned general contractor with decades of combined experience in Pittsburgh's South Hills."
>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <img src="/images/untitled-design-56.png" alt="" class="hero-bg" aria-hidden="true" fetchpriority="high" />
    <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="hero-content wrap">
      <span class="label">About Us</span>
      <h1>Built on Trust</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub text-dim">
        Licensed, insured, and referred by every client we've worked with.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Who We Are -->
  <section class="about-section">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="about-grid">
        <div class="about-text reveal">
          <h2>Who We Are</h2>
          <p class="text-dim">
            AB Brothers Construction is a licensed and insured, family-owned residential general contractor based in Pittsburgh's South Hills. With decades of combined experience, we handle everything from kitchen remodels to full-home renovations.
          </p>
          <p class="text-dim">
            We believe quality work starts with qualified professionals. Our team includes master tradesmen: plumbers, electricians, tilers, each thoroughly vetted. When you hire AB Brothers, you know exactly who's working in your home.
          </p>
          <p class="text-dim">
            Our success is measured by your satisfaction. Most of our business comes from referrals and repeat clients. We've built a reputation for showing up on time, staying on budget, and doing work that lasts.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-image reveal">
          <img
            src="/images/home-additions-pittburgh-pa.png"
            alt="Kitchen renovation with exposed brick wall, wood plank ceiling, pendant lights, and marble countertops"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <div class="about-stats">
            <div class="stat">
              <span class="stat-number">12+</span>
              <span class="stat-label">Years</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat">
              <span class="stat-number">100+</span>
              <span class="stat-label">Projects</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat">
              <span class="stat-number">5.0</span>
              <span class="stat-label">Rating</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <hr class="copper-rule" />

  <!-- Values -->
  <section class="values-section section--surface">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="values-header reveal">
        <span class="label">Our Standards</span>
        <h2>What Sets Us Apart</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="values-grid">
        <div class="value-item reveal">
          <div class="value-bar"></div>
          <h3>Premium Materials</h3>
          <p class="text-dim">
            We carefully select every product. Top-of-the-line building supplies cost a little more upfront, but our work lasts longer, saving you time and money while increasing your home's value.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-item reveal">
          <div class="value-bar"></div>
          <h3>Decades of Experience</h3>
          <p class="text-dim">
            We've seen it all. Straightforward bathroom updates, 1950s whole-home guts, tricky structural changes. That range of experience means fewer surprises and better solutions.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-item reveal">
          <div class="value-bar"></div>
          <h3>Personalized Service</h3>
          <p class="text-dim">
            Andy and Bob work closely with each customer during planning. Bob manages day-to-day project oversight. You always know who to call and what's happening.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Meet the Team -->
  <section class="team-section">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="team-header reveal">
        <span class="label">The Owners</span>
        <h2>Meet Andy & Bob</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="team-grid">
        <div class="team-card reveal">
          <div class="team-avatar">
            <span>AH</span>
          </div>
          <h3>Andy Hovanec</h3>
          <p class="text-copper team-role">Co-Owner</p>
          <a href="tel:4128551849" class="team-phone">(412) 855-1849</a>
        </div>
        <div class="team-card reveal">
          <div class="team-avatar">
            <span>BK</span>
          </div>
          <h3>Bob Krapp</h3>
          <p class="text-copper team-role">Co-Owner & Project Manager</p>
          <a href="tel:4126208821" class="team-phone">(412) 620-8821</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="team-bio text-dim reveal">
        Andrew and Bob work closely with each customer during the planning process. Bob is the project manager and primary point of contact for the duration of every job. Most of the work is done in-house, with a small group of trusted, licensed tradesmen handling electrical, drywall finishing, and HVAC.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-section section--surface">
    <div class="wrap" style="text-align: center;">
      <h2 class="reveal">Ready to Work Together?</h2>
      <p class="text-dim reveal" style="max-width: 30rem; margin: 1.25rem auto 2rem;">
        We'd love to hear about your project. Contact us for a free in-home consultation.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--copper reveal">Get in Touch</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 45vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    padding-block: 6rem 3rem;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .hero-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(
      to right,
      var(--dark) 30%,
      color-mix(in oklch, var(--dark) 70%, transparent)
    );
  }

  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .hero h1 { margin-top: 0.75rem; }

  .hero-sub {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    max-width: 28rem;
  }

  /* About section */
  .about-section {
    padding-block: var(--section-y);
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  @media (min-width: 900px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 4rem;
    }
  }

  .about-text h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-text p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .about-image img {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .about-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
  }

  .stat {
    background: var(--dark-surface);
    padding: 1.25rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .stat-number {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--copper);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .stat-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--cream-dim);
    margin-top: 0.375rem;
  }

  /* Values */
  .values-section {
    padding-block: var(--section-y);
  }

  .values-header {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .values-header h2 {
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
  }

  .values-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .values-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .value-bar {
    width: 3rem;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--copper);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .value-item h3 {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .value-item p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Team */
  .team-section {
    padding-block: var(--section-y);
  }

  .team-header {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .team-header h2 {
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
  }

  .team-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 36rem;
  }

  .team-card {
    background: var(--dark-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .team-avatar {
    width: 4.5rem;
    height: 4.5rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--dark-card);
    border: 2px solid var(--copper);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 1.25rem;

    & span {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: var(--copper);
    }
  }

  .team-card h3 {
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
  }

  .team-role {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .team-phone {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .team-phone:hover {
    color: var(--copper);
  }

  .team-bio {
    max-width: 36rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* CTA */
  .cta-section {
    padding-block: var(--section-y);
  }
</style>
